{"name":"The Lost Mines of Phandelver","content":"<p>The three Rockseeker brothers (Gundren, Tharden, and Nundro) recently located an entrance to the long-lost Wave Echo Cave, site of the mines of the @JournalEntry[Mxwg4yu7fZUgJMDK]{Phandelver's Pact}.</p>\n<p>Klarg, the bugbear who leads this goblin band, had orders to waylay Gundren. Sildar heard from the goblins that the Black Spider sent word that the dwarf was to be brought to him. Sildar doesn't know who or what the Black Spider is.</p>\n<p>Gundren had a map showing the secret location of Wave Echo Cave, but the goblins took it when they captured him. Sildar believes that Klarg sent the map and the dwarf to the chief of the Cragmaws at a place called Cragmaw Castle. Sildar doesn't know where that might be, but he suggests someone in Phandalin might know.</p>","img":"modules/lmop-shared/journal/005_-_Player_Handouts/006_-_Quests/011_-_Sildar_27s_Gear/avatar.png","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ODY1ZmU3OWIzNzY2":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.Qoh1YFJTfGnaPr10"}},"_id":"AFjUTmZf8gU3G43l"}
{"name":"Aid Gundren","content":"<p>After procuring the map and rescuing Gundren, you now have the chance to aid him in his quest to procure the power in the Forge of Spells, avenge his kin, and put a stop to the nefarious schemes of the Black Spider. And of course, the hoard of powerful magic rumored to be hidden in the mines is a rich prize.</p>","img":"modules/lmop-shared/journal/005_-_Player_Handouts/006_-_Quests/001_-_Banshee_27s_Bargain/avatar.png","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ODY1ZmU3OWIzNzY2":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.UEqa67xDOCBEXQac"}},"_id":"GP7UBQHjVMycTuUN"}
{"name":"Recovered Goods","content":"<p>The captured stores are bulky, and the characters will need a wagon to transport them. If they return the supplies to the Lionshield Coster in Phandalin (see part 2, \"Phandalin\"), they earn a reward of 50 gp and the friendship of Linene and her company.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">If the characters return the stolen goods found in area 8 of the Cragmaw hideout (or if they left the goods but reveal where they can be found), Linene gives them a reward of 50 gp and promises to help the adventurers any way she can.</section>","img":"modules/lmop-shared/journal/005_-_Player_Handouts/006_-_Quests/011_-_Sildar_27s_Gear/avatar.png","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ODY1ZmU3OWIzNzY2":3},"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":11,"handout-archived":false},"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.Sw834lnl03UZ7lcF"}},"_id":"KA6QVwvdPJzfDOMI"}
